    "description": "FreeCharge Advisory Limited is actively seeking a talented and motivated Credit Analyst to join our dynamic team in Bhubaneswar. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout FreeCharge Advisory Limited:\nFreeCharge Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FreeCharge Advisory Limited!",
